      "description": "This car is in poor condition. The exterior has significant wear including multiple dents, scratches, and rust in several areas. The interior shows heavy wear with damaged upholstery, broken trim pieces, and non-functional components. Mechanically, the car has notable issues that will require substantial repair work before reliable use.",
